metadata.name: Falling Apart Before the Finish Line
metadata.description:
Everything was fine. More than perfect.
But I crumble under the pressure.
I'm falling apart just before the finish line.
Somehow I still power through.

The "Checking In" collection was inspired by my ADHD experience. This piece, just like the others is me, checking in on my mind.

Resolution: 3000x3000px
.PNG file

ParanoidAnyway, 2022
